---
title: BBQ Veggie Hand Pies with Beyond Meat® and Apple-Spinach Salad
description: Satisfaction is found in the little things, like biting into a warm and flaky pastry! This recipe is a Beyond Meat® twist on the classic sweet and savoury BBQ pastry. Served with a crisp apple and spinach salad, this meal is sure to be a household hit for all to enjoy!
